                                <span class="footer__marketplace_name">Wildberries</span>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://www.ozon.ru/seller/ooo-vumdzhoy-25218/products/?miniapp=seller_25218" class="footer__marketplace" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">
